title: 10 French Books - April 2016 (gnv64)
description:
This torrent contains 8 French learning books in 3 different formets viz. PDF, DJVU & ePUB. It also contains 2 French newspapers (Aujourd'Hui en France) of 14th & 15th November 2015 that cover the terrorist attack in Paris:

01. French Business Dictionary
02. French Crash Course - A No-BS, Seven-Day Guide to Learning Basic French
03. French in Your Face - 1001 French Expressions (DJVU)
04. French. Language Course
05. Graded French Reader - Premiere Etape (5th Edition)
06. One Week French Mastery
07. Pardon My French!
08. Parisienne French - Chic Phrases, Slang and Style
09. Aujourd'Hui en France du Samedi 14 Novembre 2015
10. Aujourd'Hui en France du Dimanche 15 Novembre 2015
